00Z","msg":"留言好低質<br />\n<br />\n揸領航車個車手技巧極高，揸到300仲要一路睇住後面單車手個節奏黎跟<br />\n<br />\n單車手同樣技巧超乎常人，踩到二百幾仲捉得穩堂軚，仲要keep住喺一個好細嘅area唔係就會死，一膽二力三功夫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T11:57:13.000Z","msg":"上面講緊報紙佬拎環法單車賽普通踩單車黎比<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5671464d46736ac1da85171249507d448142136","tid":834401,"uid":81443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d61b8790799d7c4561f95dca6a4a431c47ef76ff","tid":834401,"uid":42453,"like":175,"dislike":3,"score":172,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T07:40:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote> <br />\n<br />\n領航車是改裝過的短程高速賽車，由曾經7次勝出Pirelli世界挑戰賽（Pirelli World Challenge）的專業車手霍爾布魯克（Shea Holbrook）駕駛。米勒科雷奈克全程要與領航車保持一致距離，要是落後太多或搖擺到滑流之外，就會撞上颶風級數的風牆受重傷。原來的紀錄保持者羅姆佩爾伯格在1988年第一次嘗試創下紀錄時，就因此而斷了24根骨頭。<br />\n<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n痴撚線 人包鐵都揸到咁快 <br />\n一抄車即刻全身骨折 <br />\n跟住又多個孝子賢孫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T11:57:31.000Z","msg":"好多範疇鬼佬都唔珍惜生命挑戰極限<br />\n所以政府獨裁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6601c2932d459e27a8298b4a3785dfa9d5155fa1","tid":834401,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T12:10:18.000Z","msg":"唔使戴氧氣罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/oh.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4191d92b7ce73167e3defc5e4a5290664af12e8","tid":834401,"uid":61115,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"1558aa29611e805a0db5a97f0f0c99fc3afae2aa","tid":834401,"uid":36087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d91c8899b8567e2ddae66b9430f59e30f0178e36","tid":834401,"uid":48817,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T09:24:18.000Z","msg":"地下有舊石仔就係咁先<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T10:09:23.000Z","msg":"一定check 過曬成個場<br />\n佢個轆郁少少都粉身碎骨"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T12:11:27.000Z","msg":"無咁易<br />\n佢用左down hill車避震前叉<br />\n<img src=\"https://c8.alamy.com/comp/PKMKGB/bonneville-utah-usa-12th-sep-2018-denise-korenek-attempts-to-break-the-cycling-world-land-speed-record-john-howard-shea-holbrook-denise-mueller-credit-action-plus-sportsalamy-live-news-PKMKGB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc8.alamy.com%2Fcomp%2FPKMKGB%2Fbonneville-utah-usa-12th-sep-2018-denise-korenek-attempts-to-break-the-cycling-world-land-speed-record-john-howard-shea-holbrook-denise-mueller-credit-action-plus-sportsalamy-live-news-PKMKGB.jpg&h=2f641150&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n加上前叉的傾角大  增加頭轆拖曳距<br />\n拖曳距愈長  穩定性愈高<br />\n無咁易受震盪而轉向<br />\n但相對降低轉向的靈活性<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.chinabike.net/uploadfile/2017/0712/20170712085027741.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinabike.net%2Fuploadfile%2F2017%2F0712%2F20170712085027741.jpg&h=2059cb0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n解決左震盪問題就到個轆既剛性問題<br />\n輪徑愈細 剛性愈强 但受障礙的影響就愈大<br />\n但佢有避震緩解左細轆既弱點<br />\n我估佢首要既考慮係避免高速情況下撞擊碎石而變形<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/qR5RnYt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FqR5RnYt.jpg&h=112c46f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n純9up"},{"pid":"893c6ac9e6688519d589228919faf41819a07921","tid":834401,"uid":198729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff6f2fea9f982a4902f1e0bc8ad56500e10c9671","tid":834401,"uid":28765,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T09:34:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/3Iz7ZMALaCY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F3Iz7ZMALaCY&d=bVbFEPqeSkte1NQq8Yo1ygRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=0bce37d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/3Iz7ZMALaCY</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T12:30:58.000Z","msg":"依招咩名堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98bcf20427250d501ff6ab8418bfa3b8998f2a7d","tid":834401,"uid":52182,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T12:45:34.000Z","msg":"睇完child登d留言先明所以香港咪難出科研<br />\n<br />\n科研其中最重要一環係不斷挑戰極限再收集數據<br />\n<br />\n再慢慢分析  科技未必一定要有目標<br